    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been very well-maintained, making it a reliable and attractive choice for a new owner. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor signs of use. While the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper consistent with careful ownership. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road without any immediate service needs.",
