    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey guys! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m selling my awesome car and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-taken care of and is ready to hit the road with a new owner! It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for commutes or weekend trips. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
