      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six engine. This unit features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing tactile mechanical engagement. The S54's individual throttle bodies offer exceptional throttle response, and the engine pulls strongly through the entire powerband. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension geometry is true, though some bushings are nearing the end of their service life. Cosmetically, the paint retains a deep luster with minor stone chips on the leading edges, consistent with a well-maintained performance vehicle of this vintage. The interior features Nappa leather with moderate bolster wear, but no punctures or structural damage to the seats.",
